#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the tree view, the bookmarks are arranged according to the categories "
"they belong to. Bookmarks without a category are located at the top level. "
"To rearrange bookmarks, the tree view offers drag and drop capabilities, so "
"you can move bookmarks around with the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Na árvore, os favoritos são organizados com base nas categorias a que "
"pertencem. Os favoritos sem categorias encontram-se no nível de topo. Para "
"reorganizar os favoritos, a árvore oferece funcionalidades de arrastamento, "
"para que possa mover os favoritos com o rato."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to edit a bookmark, you can do so by either double-clicking or "
"selecting it and pressing the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton>button. The input "
"widget will then be shown. Here you can edit the label, category name, "
"login, workgroup or domain name and the IP address."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1187
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Screenshot of the bookmark editor"
msgid "Screenshot of the bookmark editor with opened input widget"
msgstr "Imagem do editor de favoritos"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark editor with opened input widget"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1193
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to edit a bookmark, you can do so by selecting it. The stored "
#| "label, login, IP address and category name appear in the input widgets "
#| "and become editable. In most cases, you do not need to touch the IP "
#| "address and the login, because &smb4k; stores the correct values at the "
#| "time you bookmark the share. However, if the server got a different IP "
#| "address (&eg; because DHCP is used on your local network), or your login "
#| "changed, these entries should be adjusted. With the label you can give "
#| "each bookmark a custom description. It will be used for display "
#| "<emphasis>instead</emphasis> of the location, but this can be changed in "
#| "the <link linkend=\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window"
#| "\">configuration dialog</link>. Finally,the category entry helps you to "
#| "organize your bookmarks. For instance, if you use your notebook at home "
#| "and also at work, and you do not want to use <link linkend=\"profiles"
#| "\">profiles</link>, it might be a good idea to create two groups, \"Home"
#| "\" and \"Work\", and categorize the bookmarks accordingly."
msgid ""
"In most cases, you do not need to touch the IP address and the login, "
"because &smb4k; stores the correct values at the time you bookmark the "
"share. However, if the server got a different IP address (&eg; because DHCP "
"is used on your local network), or your login changed, these entries should "
"be adjusted. You also should adjust the workgroup or domain name, if its "
"name was discovered by DNS-SD (and is most likely called <emphasis>LOCAL</"
"emphasis>). With the label you can give each bookmark a custom description. "
"It will be used for display <emphasis>instead</emphasis> of the location, "
"but this can be changed in the <link linkend="
"\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window\">configuration dialog</"
"link>. Finally,the category entry helps you to organize your bookmarks. For "
"instance, if you use your notebook at home and also at work, and you do not "
"want to use <link linkend=\"profiles\">profiles</link>, it might be a good "
"idea to create two categories, \"Home\" and \"Work\", and categorize the "
"bookmarks accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Se quiser editar um favorito, podê-lo-á fazer ao seleccioná-lo. A legenda, "
"conta, endereço e nome da categoria aparecem nos campos de texto e poderão "
"ser editados. Na maioria dos casos, não terá de modificar o endereço IP e a "
"conta, porque o &smb4k; guardou os valores correctos na altura em que marcou "
"a partilha como um favorito. Contudo, se o servidor tiver um endereço IP "
"diferente (&eg; por estar a usar o DHCP na sua rede local) ou por ter mudado "
"as suas credenciais, deverá ajustar esses itens. Com a legenda, poderá dar "
"uma descrição personalizada a cada favorito. Será usado <emphasis>em vez</"
"emphasis> do endereço UNC, caso esta funcionalidade esteja activa na <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_page_user_interface_main_window\">janela de "
"configuração</link>. O item da categoria, finalmente, ajuda-o a organizar os "
"seus favoritos. Especialmente se usar &eg; o seu portátil em casa e no "
"trabalho, e não quiser usar os <link linkend=\"profiles\">perfis</link>, "
"poderá ser uma boa ideia criar duas categorias \"Casa\" e \"Trabalho\" e "
"gravar os favoritos de acordo com essa classificação."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1194
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "An entry can be removed by selecting it and clicking the "
